node.text:
The new Éire ☘️ collection designed by me from Cloak is now out.

Éire is Irish for Ireland and we wanted to make a collection celebrating my roots and heritage. We used Celtic symbols like Celtic Knots and the Celtic tree of life (Crann Bethadh). I really hope you like it, please share some stories or facts about your culture and heritage in the comments below! ☘️
